{"id": 1852, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，你都如何判断一个食物是不是健康食品？", "description": "看卖相、看标签，还是……看心情？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 2067, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170814133550C7uwIvSl6VD3xOHa.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-16T03:00:43Z", "options": [{"id": 229632, "content": "如果要百分百健康。真没多少能吃的。我母亲学营养，去超市买东西真的。好困难啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748704}, {"id": 230144, "content": "看它是谁提供的，就这么简单", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863495}, {"id": 229633, "content": "北大放在edx上的营养学课还可以，学完基本就会看了", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 302757}, {"id": 229889, "content": "大家都吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107168}, {"id": 229634, "content": "看热量。。。\n然后\n心情忐忑的吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539921}, {"id": 229635, "content": "自己的胃能否接受，后来也没有不良反应，甚至喜欢上", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1049802}, {"id": 235011, "content": "油大吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1125987}, {"id": 229636, "content": "自己做的比较放心……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658287}, {"id": 229637, "content": "看心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104566}, {"id": 230149, "content": "看感觉咯?。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107694}, {"id": 229638, "content": "贵！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652396}, {"id": 229639, "content": "一天三顿小烧烤最健康。我最爱吃的都是对我来说最健康的，我吃我爱吃的，吃完身心愉悦，无比健康。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979858}, {"id": 232455, "content": "看颜值", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1116798}, {"id": 229640, "content": "保存期限越短越好", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 860539}, {"id": 229641, "content": "看心情（＃－.－）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106412}, {"id": 231689, "content": "家里的和外面的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095310}, {"id": 229642, "content": "自己种 自己煮 自己吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1092444}, {"id": 229643, "content": "对于食物，我完全说不出一点坏话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770767}, {"id": 230155, "content": "看吃这个的人多不多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933587}, {"id": 231692, "content": "只能亲自亲为找安全。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114972}, {"id": 229645, "content": "好吃的，能吃的，就是健康的???", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1105958}, {"id": 229646, "content": "买家具看手感，买食物看心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 963982}, {"id": 229902, "content": "过期时间长短", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871628}, {"id": 229647, "content": "好吃的都是不健康的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106409}, {"id": 229648, "content": "触感\n色泽，气味\n价格和店铺环境", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106373}, {"id": 230416, "content": "靠知识，而且这些知识并不难收集和了解", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050030}, {"id": 229649, "content": "尽量吃新鲜时蔬和肉类。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104194}, {"id": 230417, "content": "少油少炸，刺身就不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108792}, {"id": 229650, "content": "看新不新鲜，看产地，看成分什么的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935032}, {"id": 229651, "content": "难吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1092823}, {"id": 229652, "content": "找个人先吃，看看有不有毒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022619}, {"id": 229653, "content": "少油少盐够新鲜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023546}, {"id": 230677, "content": "成分，颜色", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1110373}, {"id": 229654, "content": "吃不死又好吃的就是可以了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097222}, {"id": 229655, "content": "自己种自己煮自己吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104498}, {"id": 230679, "content": "感觉睡比吃更重要，充足高质量的睡眠可以带来好心情，吃嘛嘛香，身体倍棒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169623}, {"id": 229656, "content": "好不好吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1087776}, {"id": 229657, "content": "看生产日期，当然大多时候懒的看，看的最多的就是脂肪了，，，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106436}, {"id": 229658, "content": "能看出原材料的东西，看起来比较安全", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098150}, {"id": 229659, "content": "日常看看加技能系列\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166753}, {"id": 229660, "content": "看难不难吃，难以下咽又贵的，肯定健康@?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 72449}, {"id": 230684, "content": "只买贵的不买对的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039816}, {"id": 231196, "content": "保质期或赏味期", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097424}, {"id": 229661, "content": "不脏，不油腻，足矣", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201615}, {"id": 229662, "content": "吃鱼的话，看鱼眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1045217}, {"id": 230174, "content": "看卖相吧 毕竟啥也不懂，只能外观咯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028404}, {"id": 230430, "content": "看起来想吃、价格不太贵的就行，管他健康不健康", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1063594}, {"id": 229663, "content": "查资料，看科普文章。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106461}, {"id": 229919, "content": "想不想吃它的那一刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107211}, {"id": 230432, "content": "成分，时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1043839}]}